{"tid":747344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］冇理追數","createTime":"2018-07-18T09:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T10:14:35.000Z","uid":110939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e65614bb51fe5605ce6ae8bfab124d19d69859c4","tid":747344,"uid":110939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"事緣有屋企人冒用我身份，疑似拎我身份證登記左收費電視台，而電視台又唔知點解可以成功登記，好似話家人申請都得，但個名係寫我本人。<br />\n而依加屋企人不負責任冇交月費不特止，最後拖到電視停播，被收費台追討剩餘其他全數費用。<br />\n日子拖了一段時間，電視台將我的個案交由外判追數公司。<br />\n依加唔知點算好，自問唔中意欠人錢，但都冇理由係我不情願和冇用過該電視台服務底下，全數還款。<br />\n<br />\n有冇相關了解法律或個案人士比到意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dada609be06fb51b0320e75f8e14f235a4ab8b0","tid":747344,"uid":89429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"7111627ce3baaadeef1c8699c535626fd06529e7","tid":747344,"uid":110939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dada609be06fb51b0320e75f8e14f235a4ab8b0","tid":747344,"uid":89429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"報警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"報警有咩幫到我？依加啲警察見你咁case 會理咩？"},{"pid":"54169bb47e78c272ec9e39fd8112dd0ddaeec2c9","tid":747344,"uid":89429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"行使虛假文書啵"},{"pid":"5a9dc765f8fd2dd4477e2c6bd84f5e11ec9b98bc","tid":747344,"uid":8246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:10:58.000Z","msg":"你可以報警拉屋企人"},{"pid":"5f25e7cbd75e3ecead3447e016b4bd943fc7752a","tid":747344,"uid":110939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54169bb47e78c272ec9e39fd8112dd0ddaeec2c9","tid":747344,"uid":89429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"行使虛假文書啵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:11:23.000Z","msg":"咁即係反面，唔係唔得既，但父母唔想因爲咁而冇兄弟做"},{"pid":"a0c85bb017d7053a6de0a3b9739f75c0ff278f81","tid":747344,"uid":89429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"咁冇解決方法  一係迫你兄弟(?)還 <br />\n一係就自己啃左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}